skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: cambridge trivia
des:
A range of interesting facts about Cambridge, UK to make you say things like "Well, how about that?", "Blow me down with a feather!", and "Isn't that interesting?" 

We'll add new facts as they become available, so you can appear to be the king of interesting Cambridge facts at your next society benefit.
The developers have no affiliation with Cambridge University and don't represent the University in any way.
